Suggests: lingmo-connections
Description: Simple Lingmo OS app to access virtual systems
 Lingmo OS Boxes is a desktop client to view or use local virtual machines.
 Boxes is intentionally simple and easy to use.
 .
 Hardware virtualization is required.
 .
 Previously, Lingmo OS Boxes could also be used to connect to remote computers,
 but that feature is now provided by the Lingmo OS Connections app.
